channel.title: Server help, (not admin stuff or anything like that)
channel.description:
The whole day a server have been closing, well thats what it says, but how can i change server? Not numbers, but like, im on Jimmyscap2, pass: (something) but where can i find others?
Please help a poor n00b :cool: ;) :D[br][size=1]Posted at: July 19, 2006, 01:50:26 PM[/size][hr]bumped :eek: :eek:

item.title: Server help, (not admin stuff or anything like that)
item.dc:creator: @Sepranem Sepranem
item.description:
@Sepranem wrote:

theres a thread somewere in either rs2 server downloads, or in development, that has a huge list of servers…anyway, to switch servers, click “File” then “New Server” then enter the server. (and by the way, dont bump, against rules ;))
